title: Austrian Federal President pays working visit to Finland - Presidentti
snippet: Federal President of Austria Alexander Van der Bellen made a working visit to Finland accompanied by his spouse Doris Schmidauer on 3–4 April 2025. The visit was hosted by President of the Republic of Finland Alexander Stubb.
